4yg.editSummary: Slightly improved opening line for summary.
4yg.title: Arbital Quality
4yg.clickbait: Arbital's system for tracking page quality.
4yg.text:
Arbital's quality scale is used to track the quality of pages on Arbital. To request a review ask on [4ph] (#reviews) or make a comment on the page tagging [@1yq].

**Quality tags**

* [72]
* [3rk]
* [4y7]
* [4yd]
* [4yf]

**Other**

* [4ym]
* [4gs]
* [4yl]
* [4v]
* [4v4]
* [19m]
* [15r]

Although some of our tags use the same names as [Wikipedia's system](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Wikipedia/Assessment#Quality_scale) and have similar definitions, the requirements are not identical and editors from Wikipedia should not expect equivalence.

Unassessed, Stub, and Start may be used by anyone, C-Class by trusted editors, B-Class and A-Class by domain moderators, and Featured by Team Arbital.
